WEBVTT

00:04:28.760 --> 00:04:31.680
if anyone can enter it
through a connected device?

00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:36.936
You may well think,
"This will not happen to me.

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:39.560
I will just stay away
from these flawed devices."

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:42.656
But that won't keep you safe,

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:45.856
because simply by
connecting to the internet,

00:04:45.880 --> 00:04:50.456
you are put in an impossible
take-it-or-leave-it position.

00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:51.680
Let me show you.

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:55.496
Like most of you,
I have dozens of apps on my phone,

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:58.376
and used properly,
they can make our lives easier,

00:04:58.400 --> 00:05:00.840
more convenient and maybe even healthier.